node.js
-server side porgrammming,
- generally, js code run in web browser,
- node is environment that run js code outside the web browser,
- use v8 google's engine to convert the js code inot machine code,
- it run js code outside the browser so we cant access some features of js like DOM, window objects(like document.querySelector() ), localstorage,
- node porvide lot'of API's and modules like file handling, creating server etc.